# Sound Assets Directory

This directory contains audio files for the combat sound system:

- `weapons/` - Weapon fire sounds (rifle, machinegun, cannon, missile, artillery, launcher)
- `impacts/` - Impact sounds (penetration, deflection, infantry_hit, vehicle_explosion, building_hit)
- `voices/` - Unit voice lines (move_order, attack_order, under_fire, low_morale, retreating)
- `ambient/` - Ambient sounds (battle_ambient, off_screen_combat, environmental)

Audio files are referenced in `src/data/audioManifest.ts`.
Initially using placeholder paths - actual audio files to be added in later phases.
